        <item>
            <title>中国智能手机总销量跌 7%　Apple、OPPO、vivo 跌幅达双位数</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/08/apple%e3%80%81oppo%e3%80%81vivo/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple%25e3%2580%2581oppo%25e3%2580%2581vivo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/08/apple%e3%80%81oppo%e3%80%81vivo/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 15:00:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Counterpoint]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[oppo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[vivo]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1223399</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">根据外国数据机构对中国智能手机一周销售追踪报告指出，2024 年首 6 周中国智能手机整体销售量较去年同期下跌 7%，其中 Apple、OPPO 及 vivo 等厂商出现了双位数字的下滑。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1223400 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chinaweeklysmartphon-694x418.png" alt="" width="694" height="418" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chinaweeklysmartphon-694x418.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/chinaweeklysmartphon.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iPhone 的销售量比起上年同期下跌 24%，相反华为就大幅上升 64%</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Counterpoint Research 的报告指出，iPhone 在今年头几周在中国销量表现不佳。高级分析师张萌萌表示，iPhone 15 对比上代未有太大升级幅度，消费者未见想升级手机，加上高阶产品市场逐渐受到华为的威胁，中阶产品市场亦被 OPPO、vivo 和小米等公司的定价挤压，因此造成 iPhone 的销量下降。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Counterpoint Research 的数字可见，今年 iPhone 的销售量比起上年同期下跌 24%，相反华为就大幅上升 64%。中国智能手机销量整体下跌 7%，亦预计今年第一季会出现负增长。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.counterpointresearch.com/insights/china-smartphone-sales-first-6-weeks-2024-double-digit-declines-for-apple-oppo-vivo/">Counterpoint</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/24/ios-17-3-special-features/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iOS 17.3 必学功能　防盗窃 iPhone 保护 + 简单查所有 Apple 产品保养</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/09/apple-eighth-store-shanghai-opening/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国大陆第 57 间 Apple Store   本月稍后时间上海开业</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/08/epic-games-3/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 早前终止 Epic Games  开发者帐户　欧盟出手调查 Apple 或可能再被罚款</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/08/apple%e3%80%81oppo%e3%80%81vivo/mobile-phone/">中国智能手机总销量跌 7%　Apple、OPPO、vivo 跌幅达双位数</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
