            <title>Apple 早前终止 Epic Games  开发者帐户　欧盟出手调查 Apple 或可能再被罚款</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/08/epic-games-3/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=epic-games-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/08/epic-games-3/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 13:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[DMA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Epic Games]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[欧盟]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1223418</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">最近，Epic Games 计划将 Epic Games Store 和 Fortnite 引入欧洲的 iOS 装置，却发现 Apple 终止了其开发者帐户，结果引来欧盟委员会为此展开调查。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1223421 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240308at-14-694x441.png" alt="" width="694" height="441" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240308at-14-694x441.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240308at-14.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲欧盟即将就 Apple 终止 Epic Games 开发者帐户一事展开调查</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">欧盟即将就 Apple 终止 Epic Games 开发者帐户一事展开调查，评估 Apple 是否有违反数位市场法案（DMA），并要求 Apple 就事件提供解释。根据现时的数位市场法案（DMA），欧盟可向违反法案的企业收取 10% 年营利作罚款，而再次违规则可收取 20%。较早前 Apple 因与 Spotify 的纷争被欧盟罚款 18 亿欧元（约 153 亿港元）。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">早前，Epic Games 被 Apple 无故终止其开发者帐户，并认为 Apple 无意在 iOS 装置上允许真正的竞争。Epic Games 更强烈谴责 Apple 正在消灭 App Store 的潜在竞争对手。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2024/03/07/apple-epic-dev-account-dma/">Techcurnch</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/07/epic-games-apple/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 终止 Epic Games 开发者帐号　Epic Games：Apple 向我们复仇</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/19/epic-games-store/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Epic Games 将重回 iOS　今年内推出 iOS 版 Epic Games Store</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/09/epic-disney/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">迪士尼向 Epic Games 投资 118 亿，冀发展 Fortnite 宇宙</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/08/epic-games-3/software/ios-app/">Apple 早前终止 Epic Games  开发者帐户　欧盟出手调查 Apple 或可能再被罚款</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
